'''BC''' may refer to:
* [[Before Christ]], an epoch used in dating years prior to the estimated birth of Jesus

{{TOC right}}
== Geography ==
* [[Baja California]], a state in Mexico
* [[Basque Country (greater region)]], a nation between Spain and France
* [[Bell Centre]], an arena in Montreal, Quebec, Canada
* [[Botswana]]'s WMO country code and FIPS 10-4 code
* [[British Columbia]], the westernmost province of Canada

== Schools ==
* [[Bakersfield College]], a college in Bakersfield, California
* [[Baghdad College]], a high school, Baghdad, Iraq
